Description:
You arrive at a camp near the river, here you see a werewolf that was taking a nap surrounded by a few pigmen with torches and brands on their arms.

The pigmen begin to intimidate the poor werewolf and burn him with torches as he tries to escape.

For the moment, none of them have noticed you are there.
